description.en:
DAPS is a privacy coin that aims to be the most private and secure privacy coin on the market in a hybrid chain of PoW, PoSv3 and PoA. We aim to set our protocol to become the new standard of privacy coins.

What makes DAPS special is that DAPS is the first to solve the "trust problem" for fully private chains with our PoA (Proof of Audit) algorithm which audits the chain for any abnormalities without compromising the chain's anonymity features.

Stay tuned for more news soon!

Not only can you WIN part of a 145 million DAPS trading competition organised by HotBit but you can also stand a chance to WIN part of a 25 million #DAPS prize pool in the community sponsored celebration! 🏆🌟

Support us and let's make this our biggest promo ever and support privacy!

https://gleam.io/fiSih/daps-hotbit-listing-celebration-25-million-prize-pool-2020

Version 1.0.5 is here! 🥳

Stuck on a fork? No more messing with block hashes.
Now you can enter the Debug Console and use resync from BlockNumber to get back on track.

Need to rescan? Simpler rescan function added.
Jump into the Debug Console and enter rescan to have your whole wallet rescanned.

Not interested in Staking or Masternodes?
Set litemode=1 in your dapscoin.conf to enable “Lite Mode” with these functions turned off. https://officialdapscoin.com/daps-coin-v1-0-5

We've reached over 3000 masternodes so far!

We are making good progress with our chain and wallets finally getting stable with V1.0.3 release recently.

Read more about the fixes and plans: https://officialdapscoin.com/what-to-expect-from-daps-coin-update-v103/

Grab V1.0.3: https://officialdapscoin.com/daps-coin-v103-update/
